		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Alice Bradley</span></strong> lives with her husband and son in Brooklyn, New York. She is the author of one of the top-ranked parenting blogs on the Web (<a href="http://www.finslippy.com">www.finslippy.com</a>) and co-creator of the website Let&rsquo;s Panic about Babies!&nbsp; (www.lets-panic.com). Her writing has been published in the <em>Berkeley Fiction Review</em>, <em>Fence</em>, and <em>Good Housekeeping</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/alice-bradley" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
