				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/226/anatomy-of-a-lie">Anatomy Of A Lie</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/diana-greene">Diana Greene</a></li><li><a href="/issues/226">October 1994</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


														<a href="/issues/226" class="block-content-photo cover-thumb">
					
					<img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg' viewBox%3D'0 0 557 728'%2F%3E"
